Ya.

00:25:51.310 --> 00:25:53.540
Silakan masuk. Dia menunggumu.

00:25:57.009 --> 00:25:58.550
Selamat datang, Direktur Woo.

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:00.019
Aku Choi Hyung Sun.

00:26:01.120 --> 00:26:02.290
Aku Woo Seung Hui.

00:26:02.390 --> 00:26:03.949
Aku bukan direktur, tapi wakil direktur.

00:26:05.159 --> 00:26:07.189
Seingatku, kamu seorang direktur.

00:26:07.320 --> 00:26:09.890
Di Victory Academy, nama lama Daechi Chase.

00:26:13.860 --> 00:26:14.969
Mau duduk?

00:26:41.530 --> 00:26:42.759
Anda gugup?

00:26:43.630 --> 00:26:45.900
Aku meminta bertemu

00:26:46.360 --> 00:26:48.570
